I haven't got my purse with me.
That's alright, Miss Ann.
The government can wait.
Thank you, Abe. Very much.
Good morning, Miss Ann.
My, you're looking prettier every day.
Good news, I hope.
Very good, thank you.
Ha! Catch me waiting two years for any man.
